      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained, making it a reliable choice for its next owner. The engine and transmission operate smoothly, and all essential electronics and safety features are fully functional. While you may find some minor cosmetic imperfections consistent with regular use, the interior is clean and the car drives excellently. It offers a great balance of performance and value for anyone seeking a dependable daily driver.",
